N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4217.3 - Prerequisites

State Regulations

In order to win a daily double, it is necessary for the
purchaser of daily double ticket to select the winners of each of the two races
specified for the daily double. If either of his selections fails to win, his
contract is voided, except as provided in this Part. Notes
